spec_data.Name: python2-unittest2
spec_data.Description:
unittest2 is a backport of the new features added to the unittest testing
framework in Python 2.7 and onwards. It is tested to run on Python 2.6, 2.7,
3.2, 3.3, 3.4 and pypy.

spec_data.Summary: The new features in unittest backported to Python 2.4+
